+      . . . .
+    `);
+    // S=(0,1), (1,1)=^
+    // splits: down-left: (2,0),(3,-1) absorbed; down-right: (2,2),(3,3)
+    // visited: (0,1),(1,1),(2,0),(2,2),(3,3)
+    expect(countBeamCells(g)).toBe(5);
